detail_description_1: Bébé Bath Oceane loves to splish-splash and play with her cute frog friend in the water!
detail_description_2: The doll's head and limbs are made of soft vinyl that is lightly scented with vanilla, a Corolle signature
detail_description_3: Whether its music or dance, Kavi loves performing. She even choreographs a Bollywood routine with her friends for their school revue. With so much excitement, can Kavi find a way to stay on top of her schoolwork and get her dance moves down before the curtain goes up?

detail_description_1: An 18 Kavi™ doll with brown eyes that open and close, and medium-length layered dark-brown hair styled in a half ponytail. She has a soft cotton body, and her movable head and limbs are made of smooth vinyl.
detail_description_2: A layered, cropped mesh top with a multicolored print; silver jogger-style pants; pink tennis shoes; and cotton underwear
detail_description_3: Nicki is a very pretty doll and Im glad that the Marie Grace face mold was brought back for her. I had just gotten the new Truly me 119 with that face mold right before Kavi came out and I was a little upset that they looked so similar.
